      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "Is it ok that this static initialization happens before 'official' OpenSSL initialization, even before main()?\nWhat will happen if secp256k1 is not built into OpenSSL? I don't think it will reach the sanity check anymore.\n",
